messages.content: Hi! How can I help you today?

Hello! I recently moved to a new house on Elm Avenue in Houston, and I have two things I need help with. First, I have an order that was mistakenly sent to my old address, and I want to change the delivery address to my new home. Second, I want to update my user default address to the new home as well. Could you please look up my orders and help me with these address changes? Also, after that, I would like to exchange a tablet I bought for the cheapest one available due to moving costs. I prefer not to reveal my address details directly, so I hope you can find the information from my orders.
